<TEXT>
   A young man opened fire on a brother and
sister today in a courtyard of a high school in this Paris suburb,
seriously wounding both of them and then killing himself, officials
said.
   Samir Doulim shot Abil Jbali and Jbali's half-sister Ilham Jbali,
before turning his pistol on himself, assistant prosecutor Michele
