<HEAD>Ambassador Reprimanded for Part in Nuclear Debate</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BERN, Switzerland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Switzerland's former ambassador to
Mexico has been reprimanded for airing his views on nuclear power in
