<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Liberian-registered chemical tanker exploded and
burst into flames off central Japan on Tuesday, and 23 crew members
were reported missing, a coast guard official said.
   The 23,038-ton Maasgusar, which was carrying methanol and other
highly flammable liquids, ``is still burning and explosions are
