   ACTOR: Gene Hackman, ``Mississippi Burning''; Tom Hanks, ``Big'';
Dustin Hoffman, ``Rain Man''; Edward James Olmos, ``Stand and
Deliver''; Max von Sydow, ``Pelle the Conqueror.''
